Text:
Ini bukan di Padang Ipoh, Ipoh tapi di Kampung Padang Ipoh, Kuala Berang, Terengganu. Sebuah lori Angkatan Pertahanan Awam Malaysia (APM) terbalik dibawa arus deras, hari ini.

Lori tersebut membawa bantuan makanan utk dihantar kpd mangsa banjir.  

📸Mohd Khairul Fikiri/Bernama https://t.co/rPsov1YpEj
Translated_Tweets:
This is not in Padang Ipoh, Ipoh but in Kampung Padang Ipoh, Kuala Berang, Terengganu. A Malaysian Civil Defense Force (APM) truck was turned upside down today.

The truck brought food assistance to be delivered to flood victims.

📸Mohd Khairul Fikiri/Bernama https://t.co/rpsov1ypej

Text:
Semalam, MUDA Puchong bersama @MUDAxBangi ke Kolej Universiti Islam Selangor (KUIS) untuk membantu pelajar-pelajar mendapatkan makanan kerana di kuarantin. 

Bantuan yang telah disampaikan
- 50 pek makanan (roti, biskut dan lain-lain)
- 60 kotak air mineral https://t.co/nbzfcFYixD
Translated_Tweets:
Yesterday, Young Puchong with @mudaxbangi to the Selangor Islamic University College (KUIS) to help students get food in quarantine.

Helps that have been delivered
- 50 packs of food (bread, biscuits etc.)
- 60 boxes of mineral water https://t.co/nbzfcfyixd
